== Hindi ==

=== Pronunciation ===
usually representing the sound / j /, often transliterated as y. Pronounced alone it is / jə / like the beginning of the English word [[yum]].

===Definition===

The first semivowel of the [[Devanagari]] script. Linguistically it is considered the [[w:palatal approximant|palatal approximant]].

